extends includes/layout
include includes/mixin

block content
    .container.mt-5
      //- breadcrumbs
      nav(aria-label='breadcrumb')
        ol.breadcrumb
          li.breadcrumb-item
            a(href='#') Home
          li.breadcrumb-item
            a(href='#') Shop
          li.breadcrumb-item.active(aria-current='page') Gravda sagittis felism
    
    .container.single-product-content
      .row.large-gutters
        .col-lg-6
          .single-product-images.popup-gallery
            img(src='assets/images/products/1.jpg', alt='Product Image', width='800', height='893')
            ul.product-images-gallery
              li
                img(src='assets/images/products/20.jpg', alt='Product image', width='800', height='893')
              li
                img(src='assets/images/products/2.jpg', alt='Product image', width='800', height='893')
              li
                img(src='assets/images/products/4.jpg', alt='Product image', width='800', height='893')
              li
                img(src='assets/images/products/21.jpg', alt='Product image', width='800', height='893')
            .clearfix
        .col-lg-6
          .single-product-content.mt-lg-0
            h1.entry-title.product-title Gravda sagittis felism
            .single-product-price $9.85
            .single-product-rating
              span.rating.mr-2
                span.fas.fa-star
                span.fas.fa-star
                span.fas.fa-star
                span.fas.fa-star-half-alt
                span.far.fa-star
              a.rating-count(href='#') (2 customer review)
            .single-product-description
              p I love things that age well - things that dont date, that stand the test of time and that become living examples of the absolute best. You have a more interesting life if you wear impressive clothes.
              p I think there is something about luxury - it's not something people need, but it's what they want. 
            .add-to-cart-warp
              .quantity.d-flex
                input.form-control.qty.total-quantity(type='number', step='1', min='1', name='quantity', value='1', title='Qty', size='2')
              a.btn.btn-dark.btn-add-cart.rounded-1(href='#') Add To Cart 
              .clearfix
            ul.single-product-meta
              li
                span SKU: 
                  span 007
              li
                span Category: 
                  span Clothes
              li
                span Tags: 
                  span Top, Dress
      // Tabs
      hr.mt-5.mb-6
      .row
        .col-md-3.mb-4.mb-md-0
          #v-pills-tab.nav.flex-column.nav-pills(role='tablist', aria-orientation='vertical')
            a#description-tab.nav-link.active(data-toggle='pill', href='#description', role='tab', aria-controls='description', aria-selected='true') Description
            a#additional-information-tab.nav-link(data-toggle='pill', href='#additional-information', role='tab', aria-controls='additional-information', aria-selected='false')  Additional Information
            a#reviews-tab.nav-link(data-toggle='pill', href='#reviews', role='tab', aria-controls='reviews', aria-selected='false')  Reviews
        .col-md-9
          #v-pills-tabContent.tab-content
            #description.tab-pane.fade.show.active(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='description-tab')
              p I don't really know how to do casual clothes. I try as much as possible to give you a great basic product and what comes out, I feel, is really amazing. I don't care about money. I really don't care. I just want to do what I do. Fashion fades, only style remains the same.
              p I think in the darkest moments, we need a break. I don't like trends. They tend to make everybody look the same. My job is to bring out in people what they wouldn't dare do themselves. The important thing is to take your time and not get stressed.
            #additional-information.tab-pane.fade(role='tabpanel', aria-labelledby='additional-information-tab')
